sources.title: Odessa In Flacari Catuse Rosii 1942 Odessa In Fiamme
sources.description: Odessa in flacari (Catuse rosii)(1942)(Odessa in fiamme) Film artistic despre intrarea comunistilor in Basarabia. O productie romano-italiana. Are subtitrare in limba romana pe film. Audio - italian. Video - romanian hardsubbed.
